[{'text': 'This video shows how to print using your Windows
8 tablet and an HP Jetdirect 2800w NFC, or', 'start': 1.88, 'duration': 8.13}, {'text': 'Near Field Communication, enabled printer.
In this video we demonstrate the steps using', 'start': 10.01, 'duration': 5.22}, {'text': 'the HP Elite Pad 900 and the HP LaserJet Enterprise
Flow MFP M830 printer.', 'start': 15.23, 'duration': 7.0}, {'text': 'Before beginning, the HP Jetdirect 2800w NFC
and Wireless Direct Accessory must be installed', 'start': 25.48, 'duration': 7.0}, {'text': 'on your printer. We will not give those instructions
in this video.', 'start': 32.509, 'duration': 5.831}, {'text': 'If you have not already done so, verify 
your HP printer is ready to print using HP', 'start': 38.34, 'duration': 5.75}, {'text': 'Jetdirect 2800w NFC/Wireless Direct Accessory.
Make sure the printer is in the Ready state.', 'start': 44.09, 'duration': 7.0}, {'text': 'Print the configuration pages from the control
panel to confirm that NFC and HP Wireless', 'start': 54.89, 'duration': 5.71}, {'text': 'Direct printing are enabled on the printer.
If a page titled Wireless is included, then', 'start': 60.6, 'duration': 15.5}, {'text': 'NFC and HP Wireless Direct printing are enabled.
Make sure that the latest version of HP ePrint', 'start': 76.1, 'duration': 7.8}, {'text': 'Software is installed on your Windows 8 tablet.
It should be version 4.5 or newer.', 'start': 83.9, 'duration': 6.73}, {'text': 'Note: ARM-based tablets running Windows RT
are not supported.', 'start': 90.63, 'duration': 5.829}, {'text': 'Next, set up the wireless connection on your
tablet so it can connect to the Wireless Direct', 'start': 96.459, 'duration': 6.04}, {'text': 'Accessory.
It is important to know where the WiFi antenna', 'start': 102.499, 'duration': 4.68}, {'text': 'is located on your wireless device so that
you can align it correctly with the Jetdirect', 'start': 107.179, 'duration': 5.19}, {'text': "2800w NFC during the initial connection process.
Verify that your device's wireless capability", 'start': 112.369, 'duration': 8.59}, {'text': 'is enabled.
This is typically found in the Settings menu.', 'start': 120.959, 'duration': 5.04}, {'text': 'You must disconnect from any existing wireless
connection (wireless LAN or Internet) to print', 'start': 125.999, 'duration': 6.141}, {'text': "using the NFC.
From your tablet's application, select the", 'start': 132.14, 'duration': 4.79}, {'text': 'File menu,
and then select Print.', 'start': 136.93, 'duration': 4.74}, {'text': 'From the list of available printers, select
HP ePrint.', 'start': 141.67, 'duration': 5.27}, {'text': "Next, closely align or touch the HP Jetdirect
2800w NFC icon and your tablet's antenna.", 'start': 146.94, 'duration': 8.76}, {'text': 'They must be within 1 inch or 2.5 cm of each
other.', 'start': 155.7, 'duration': 4.81}, {'text': 'Hold your tablet on or near the HP Jetdirect
2800w for at least one full second.', 'start': 160.51, 'duration': 7.0}, {'text': 'The tablet might make a connection sound or
display a pop-up symbol.', 'start': 168.38, 'duration': 7.0}, {'text': "Once a connection is established, the HP ePrint
Software displays the HP wireless direct printer's", 'start': 176.05, 'duration': 6.23}, {'text': 'name.
Tap the Settings button to define basic print', 'start': 182.28, 'duration': 3.79}, {'text': 'options such as the number of copies, pages
per sheet, and printing on one or both sides', 'start': 186.07, 'duration': 6.27}, {'text': '(also known as duplex).
Tap Print.', 'start': 192.34, 'duration': 5.36}, {'text': 'Your print job will be sent to the printer.
Note: HP ePrint Software saves the printer', 'start': 197.7, 'duration': 16.17}, {'text': 'to your recently used printers list located
on the Recent tab.', 'start': 213.87, 'duration': 4.78}, {'text': 'You may select Automatically print upon successful
connection, so that future print jobs will', 'start': 218.65, 'duration': 5.33}, {'text': 'print automatically when you touch your tablet
to the HP printer. If this option is selected', 'start': 223.98, 'duration': 6.23}, {'text': 'the Settings option will not be not available.
For additional information about HP ePrint', 'start': 230.21, 'duration': 6.64}, {'text': 'Software including frequently asked questions,
go to: www.hp.com/go/eprintsoftware.', 'start': 236.85, 'duration': 10.2}, {'text': 'Click Documentation to download the user guide.
For additional setup, configuration, and troubleshooting', 'start': 247.569, 'duration': 8.031}, {'text': 'information, go to www.hp.com/go/jd2800wSupport
or scan the QR code shown on the screen with', 'start': 255.6, 'duration': 12.71}, {'text': 'your mobile device.
You can find additional helpful videos at', 'start': 268.31, 'duration': 4.59}, {'text': 'hp.com/supportvideos and on our YouTube channel,
youtube.com/hpprintersupport.', 'start': 272.9, 'duration': 9.919}]

[{'text': 'The response to the disaster in Haiti is 24/7
from around the world.', 'start': 1.43, 'duration': 4.88}, {'text': 'The airport is a scene of international commitment,
as supplies and personnel arrive on a continual', 'start': 6.31, 'duration': 5.61}, {'text': 'basis with one objective in mind:
to help.', 'start': 11.92, 'duration': 4.59}, {'text': "For the initial elements of the 82nd Airborne
Division, it's time to get to work.", 'start': 16.51, 'duration': 4.05}, {'text': '>>Our objective is to get out there and provide
security', 'start': 20.56, 'duration': 2.18}, {'text': 'and to begin providing humanitarian aid
and relief supplies out to the local populous.', 'start': 22.74, 'duration': 5.12}, {'text': '>>[McCabe] According to latest reports, the
death toll could rise as high as 100,000,', 'start': 27.86, 'duration': 4.85}, {'text': 'easy to imagine when you see the horrific
damage caused by the massive earthquake.', 'start': 32.71, 'duration': 4.55}, {'text': 'Destruction can be seen throughout the country,
especially in Port-au-Prince.', 'start': 37.26, 'duration': 4.31}, {'text': 'The rule book for a humanitarian operation
of this magnitude', 'start': 41.57, 'duration': 5.89}, {'text': 'is being written and updated constantly.
The critical element, according to all, is', 'start': 47.46, 'duration': 5.099}, {'text': "communication and coordination.
>>There's confusion right now,", 'start': 52.559, 'duration': 3.361}, {'text': "but I think in another day or two it'll be
more organized.", 'start': 55.92, 'duration': 3.81}, {'text': ">>[soldier on bullhorn] Ladies and gentlemen,
si'l vous plait.", 'start': 59.73, 'duration': 2.54}, {'text': '>>[McCabe] Lines of survivors gather outside
the airport, looking to get out.', 'start': 62.27, 'duration': 4.5}, {'text': '>>Now is the worst day. Every day--right now,
morning, night.', 'start': 66.77, 'duration': 3.95}, {'text': ">>We're just trying to figure this out as
we go", 'start': 70.72, 'duration': 2.43}, {'text': 'with the guidance we get.
Guidance is continually changing because all', 'start': 73.15, 'duration': 4.07}, {'text': 'of the processes around here
are still getting fine-tuned.', 'start': 77.22, 'duration': 2.81}, {'text': "But we're doing the best we can. It seems
to be working all right.", 'start': 80.03, 'duration': 2.46}, {'text': '>>[soldier] Form lines, please.
>>[McCabe] All nonessential foreign personnel', 'start': 82.49, 'duration': 3.89}, {'text': "are being evacuated.
>>We're sorry to leave them in their situation,", 'start': 86.38, 'duration': 3.95}, {'text': "but there's not really much we can do anymore
except get out of the way", 'start': 90.33, 'duration': 3.45}, {'text': 'and let them get started on their recovery.
>>[McCabe] The death toll may never be known,', 'start': 93.78, 'duration': 5.1}, {'text': "but it's estimated one-third of Haiti's almost
nine million population", 'start': 98.88, 'duration': 3.96}, {'text': 'were directly impacted by the earthquake.
The U.S. Military, in conjunction with the', 'start': 102.84, 'duration': 4.86}, {'text': 'international community,
is bringing order to the chaos caused by this', 'start': 107.7, 'duration': 3.849}, {'text': 'natural disaster.
Immediate relief efforts are increasing.', 'start': 111.549, 'duration': 4.621}, {'text': 'For the people of Haiti, these are signs of
hope in a time of despair.', 'start': 116.17, 'duration': 5.05}, {'text': 'Gail McCabe, Port-au-Prince, Haiti.', 'start': 121.22, 'duration': 1.97}]
